  "text": "In the 14 Bev-D patients with tumor recurrence, the pattern of progression was predominately local disease, followed by diffuse progression and distant failure. [CITATION_1] In contrast, of the 61 Bev-S patients with radiographic progression, the pattern of progression was predominately diffuse, followed by local disease, distant, and multifocal failure (Table 4 , Supplementary Figure) . These differences in patterns of disease progression between Bev-D and Bev-S patients were statistically significant (P ¼ .079), especially when distant failure and multifocal failure were combined (P ¼ .036).",
