      "span_text": "In the 14 Bev-D patients with tumor recurrence, the pattern of progression was predominately local disease, followed by diffuse progression and distant failure.  In contrast, of the 61 Bev-S patients with radiographic progression, the pattern of progression was predominately diffuse, followed by local disease, distant, and multifocal failure (Table 4 , Supplementary Figure) .",
